40 (5.2) 'Property manager' means a licensee who performs property management services
41 for a specific property.
42 (5.3) 'Residential rental property' means any property that is rented or leased as a
43 dwelling unit for human habitation. Such term does not include homes licensed by the
44 Department of Community Health pursuant to Code Sections 31-7-12, 31-7-12.2, and
